Package it.polimi.ingsw.controller

Class Controller

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.controller.Controller
All Implemented Interfaces:
LambdaObserver
public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
implements LambdaObserver
This class represents the Controller of the MVC Architectural pattern. It observes the View and gets notified whenever the user submits an input in order to handle it.
